				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Karlach has been sent to prison after deciding to attack Gortash while the steelwatcher is present and now has to be recruited again in Wyrm's prison if players get to free her. She is unhappy - she tried to go after him and failed. She's beating herself up inside and that's manifesting itself in anger."
